description:
# vat python utilities

## using
install:
```
pip install vat-utils
```

## developing
install dev requirements:
```
poetry install
```

run tests with tox:
```
poetry run tox
```

build:
```
poetry build
```

publish to pypi:
```
poetry publish
```
